12:01.969 --> 12:04.030
which meaning you give
to these pieces.

12:04.030 --> 12:07.200
Much more interesting
is this process.

12:07.200 --> 12:09.369
What happens if,
suddenly,

12:09.369 --> 12:11.999
one of these pieces
that defines us...

12:11.999 --> 12:16.170
starts to tumble?

12:16.170 --> 12:18.670
Well, of course, we adapt.

12:18.670 --> 12:22.499
And sometimes, we even have
to make some basic changes.

12:22.499 --> 12:24.469
<i>♪ ♪</i>

12:24.469 --> 12:27.800
But if all these pieces
work well together...

12:29.900 --> 12:32.900
then it is always possible...

12:37.499 --> 12:39.999
To form a unit...

12:41.499 --> 12:43.999
And once again...

12:48.599 --> 12:51.430
To achieve harmony.

12:51.430 --> 12:53.129
Thank you.

12:53.129 --> 12:55.900
[applause]

12:55.999 --> 12:57.999
But life is never that easy,

12:57.999 --> 13:01.070
and destiny always has
new challenges for us.

13:01.070 --> 13:04.570
But you could say that,
from time to time...

13:05.830 --> 13:09.029
Destiny brings us
something new...

13:09.029 --> 13:12.229
that we have to arrange with.

13:12.229 --> 13:14.229
But how to include
this new element

13:14.229 --> 13:17.170
into our perfect,
uh, composition?

13:17.170 --> 13:18.999
I mean, every space is filled,

13:18.999 --> 13:21.029
and it is already well-stocked.

13:21.029 --> 13:24.600
So this whole unit
slowly starts to crack...

13:24.600 --> 13:27.529
under the pressure
of the new experience.

13:27.529 --> 13:32.070
And sometimes, it even
all breaks down to pieces.

13:32.070 --> 13:34.830
Midlife crisis,
a quarter-life crisis,

13:34.830 --> 13:38.200
or something in between,
and we have to ask ourselves,

13:38.200 --> 13:41.670
"How do we find
that harmonic shape again?"

13:41.670 --> 13:43.830
<i>[exotic dramatic music playing]</i>

13:43.830 --> 13:45.600
Well...

13:45.600 --> 13:47.670
with a little...

13:47.670 --> 13:51.330
self-reflection...

13:51.330 --> 13:54.869
and patience...

13:54.869 --> 13:57.200
with self-confidence...

13:57.200 --> 13:59.430
<i>♪ ♪</i>

13:59.430 --> 14:02.070
and effort...

14:02.070 --> 14:04.769
it is possible to integrate

14:04.769 --> 14:08.899
any new piece
into this arrangement...

14:10.470 --> 14:13.670
And still...

14:13.670 --> 14:17.029
form that wonderful shape...

14:17.029 --> 14:18.999
that makes it so unique.

14:18.999 --> 14:21.999
[applause]

14:25.470 --> 14:28.499
But life is a series
of challenges

14:28.499 --> 14:30.399
more and more challenging,

14:30.399 --> 14:33.700
and, um, it has always
new things for us,

14:33.700 --> 14:36.269
sometimes even bigger
and more unexpected

14:36.269 --> 14:39.399
than we are prepared
to handle.

14:39.399 --> 14:41.129
But...

14:41.129 --> 14:45.470
you know,
to conquer these challenges...

14:45.470 --> 14:47.800
all we have to do
is sometimes...

14:47.800 --> 14:50.269
<i>♪ ♪</i>

14:50.269 --> 14:54.399
Change our point of view...

14:54.399 --> 14:57.830
to see things differently...

15:00.970 --> 15:03.999
In order to come up...

15:03.999 --> 15:06.629
with a solution.

15:06.629 --> 15:09.629
[cheering and applause]

15:13.700 --> 15:15.500
And now, perhaps,
you understand

15:15.500 --> 15:17.100
that it's not about the size

15:17.100 --> 15:19.029
or the position
of these pieces,

15:19.029 --> 15:21.929
nor about the significance
we place on them,

15:21.929 --> 15:26.500
but rather about this harmonic
composition they form.

15:26.500 --> 15:28.330
<i>♪ ♪</i>

15:28.330 --> 15:31.929
And of course,
most importantly,

15:31.929 --> 15:36.269
that everything fits perfectly

15:36.269 --> 15:39.629
within the framework...

15:39.629 --> 15:41.169
of our lives.

15:41.169 --> 15:44.730
[cheering and applause]

15:44.730 --> 15:47.669
- Patrick Folkerts!

15:47.669 --> 15:49.500
- Thank you!

15:49.500 --> 15:51.470
Please.
- Oh, thank you.

15:51.470 --> 15:53.769
You must be so good
at organizing.

15:53.769 --> 15:55.970
- I'm glad that it seems
