37:03.020 --> 37:04.179
you can tell the truth--

37:04.179 --> 37:06.049
I just have to ask you
one question, Kim.

37:06.049 --> 37:08.119
- Yes.
- Do you see the egg?

37:08.119 --> 37:09.420
- Yes.
- Good.

37:09.420 --> 37:10.520
- I don't wanna break the egg.
[laughter]

37:10.520 --> 37:11.819
- Now watch this, Kim.

37:11.819 --> 37:14.080
This is the closest
you'll ever experience...

37:14.080 --> 37:17.080
to real magic.
- [exhales sharply]

37:17.080 --> 37:18.250
- Do you feel it, Kim?

37:18.250 --> 37:20.650
Because that egg is gone...
- [gasps]

37:20.650 --> 37:22.150
- Gone, gone.
[audience exclaims]

37:22.150 --> 37:24.150
And don't take
our word for it, Kim,

37:24.150 --> 37:25.650
check his pockets!

37:25.650 --> 37:27.549
Check his sleeves!

37:27.549 --> 37:29.920
That is gone, gone.

37:29.920 --> 37:31.480
- That is gone.

37:31.480 --> 37:32.819
- Okay.
- Oh, my God.

37:32.819 --> 37:34.750
If you check any more, Kim,

37:34.750 --> 37:36.549
you can't be in the Senate.
- I know!

37:36.549 --> 37:37.549
[laughter]

37:37.549 --> 37:38.949
I was trying
to be very careful.

37:38.949 --> 37:41.949
- Now, Kim, that still happened
in your hands,

37:41.949 --> 37:44.179
but Teller
was awfully near to you.

37:44.179 --> 37:45.819
If that were real magic,

37:45.819 --> 37:48.520
it could happen
when you're alone.

37:48.520 --> 37:50.449
One last time, Kim,
take a look in the bag.

37:50.449 --> 37:52.049
Do you see the snowy-white egg

37:52.049 --> 37:53.219
in the dark interior
of the bag?

37:53.219 --> 37:55.080
- No.
- Do you feel the egg

37:55.080 --> 37:56.449
in the bag?
- No.

37:56.449 --> 37:57.850
- So you can't see it,
you can't feel it.

37:57.850 --> 38:00.449
You gotta hold it.
Hold it just like that, Kim.

38:00.449 --> 38:02.619
Now, Kim, do you feel alone
here on stage?

38:02.619 --> 38:03.719
We'll move a little further
away from you.

38:03.719 --> 38:05.279
- Okay.
- Feel alone now, Kim?

38:05.279 --> 38:06.350
- Yes.
- We'll move

38:06.350 --> 38:07.449
a little further away.

38:07.449 --> 38:09.449
Now, Kim,
you checked completely,

38:09.449 --> 38:11.580
but one last time,
little peek in the bag.

38:12.980 --> 38:14.679
Do you see the egg in the bag?
- No.

38:14.679 --> 38:16.580
- Kim, keep holding--

38:16.580 --> 38:17.980
keep holding
with your right hand.

38:17.980 --> 38:19.420
Let go with your left.
- Just with my right hand?

38:19.420 --> 38:22.350
- Teller, magic!

38:22.350 --> 38:23.350
[snaps fingers]

38:23.350 --> 38:26.380
Kim, show your left hand empty.

38:26.380 --> 38:29.219
Slowly, carefully,
reach in the bag.

38:29.219 --> 38:30.679
- I'm gonna cry.
- Reach in the bag.

38:30.679 --> 38:32.549
- [gasps]
- Be careful, Kim,

38:32.549 --> 38:33.750
[laughter]

38:33.750 --> 38:35.750
- It's here!
- It's a real egg.

38:35.750 --> 38:38.049
Kim Raver!
[cheering and applause]

38:38.049 --> 38:40.619
- That's amazing.
You guys are amazing.

38:40.619 --> 38:41.819
- That's Kim Raver
right there.

38:41.819 --> 38:42.949
[Alyson laughing]

38:42.949 --> 38:46.150
[cheering and applause]

38:46.150 --> 38:47.819
That was so good.

38:47.819 --> 38:49.779
- That's amazing.
- Ah!

38:49.779 --> 38:51.750
That's a wrap
on tonight's show,

38:51.750 --> 38:53.350
but we'll come back
with another one

38:53.350 --> 38:54.779
before you know it!

38:54.779 --> 38:58.819
From all of us at "Fool Us,"
goodnight from Las Vegas!

